{"id": 5237, "title": "Ticket #5237: Improvements to condor_status for 8.5 series", "description": "<blockquote>\ncondor_status should be improved in the 8.5 series.\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>it should understand static, partitionable and dynamic slots\n\n<p></p></li><li>it should summarize the pool by default\n\n<p></p></li><li>it should allow for wildcards in the projection list\n\n<p></p></li><li>it should allow support group-by (autocluster) queries like condor_q does\n\n<p></p></li><li>sorting does not add sort attributes to projection list\n\n<p></p></li><li>other stuff I haven't thought of yet\n</li></ul>\n\n<p></p><div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" summary=\"EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets\">\n<caption>\n  <a href=\"rptview?rn=86\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets\">EMBED: Status Table of Derived Tickets</a>\n</caption>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"11\"><form action=\"rptview\" method=\"GET\">\n<input name=\"rn\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"86\"/>\nTN: <input name=\"TN\" type=\"text\" value=\"5237\"/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Go\"/>\n</form></td></tr> \n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=2&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Developer</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=3&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">#</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=4&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Status</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=5&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Type</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=6&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Pri</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=7&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Created</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=8&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Changed</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=9&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Target</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&amp;order_by=10&amp;order_dir=ASC&amp;TN=5237\">Due Date</a></th>\n<th><a href=\"rptview?rn=86&